Package gate.compound.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCompoundDocument
    This is an abstract implementation of the AbstractAlignedDocument This class overrides the methods of DocumentImpl and provide generic implementation of some of the methods of AlignedDocument
    AnnotationStream
    AnnotationStream is a helper class that helps in combining multiple documents into a single composite document.
    CompoundDocumentFromXml
    Those compound documents saved in a single xml document can be reloaded in GATE using this LR.
    CompoundDocumentImpl
    Implemention of the CompoundDocument.
    DeleteMemberPR
    This PR deletes a member document from the compound document.
    SwitchMemberPR
    This PR allows switching the focus of the compound document to its various member documents.
